A native Cocoa application for calculating girth, volumetric weight and for tracking parcels. Itâ€™s designed for Mac OS X, Snow Leopard (or higher) is required. This work is released under a FreeBSD license variant. Feature overview:

- calculation of girth and volumetric weight
- parcel tracking: DHL, DPD, FedEx, GLS, Hermes, ParcelForce, Royal Mail, UPS
- Direct Parcel Distribution conformity tests
- Sparkle software update
- user preferences
- beautiful designed graphical user interface
- integrated help
- multi-language: English and German

